Firefighters are battling the blaze that is now threatening farm property in the Bredasdorp area. CAPE TOWN - A fire in Bredasdorp is still raging.Firefighters are battling the blaze that is now threatening farm property.Two guesthouses have already been evacuated as a precaution.Overberg fire chief Reinard Geldenhuys.&quot;Right now we've got a big fire burning close to Bredasdorp, burning on multiple fronts, threatening farmlands and farm structures. We've got various units on the ground and aerial units and probably about 100 landowners in their vehicles.&quot;(Edited by Zunaid Ismael)